  "texts": [
    "This hybrid structure ensures robust learning and prediction capabilities, accommodating the unpredictability of real-world dynamics while preserving information continuity.",
    "By marrying the strengths of RNNs with the flexibility of State Space Models (SSM) [54], RSSM establishes a comprehensive framework for world models, enhancing their ability to predict future states with a balance of precision and adaptability.We denote the sequence of observations and actions as (x 0, a 1, x 1, a 2, x 2,..., a T, x T).",
    "Namely, the agent takes action a t+1 after observing x t, and receives the next observation x t+1.",
    "We omit the reward for simplicity.",
    "RSSM models the observations and state transitions through the following generative process:p (x 0:T | a 1:T) = T t=0 p (x t | z ≤t, a ≤t) p (z t | z <t, a ≤t) dz 0:T (1)where z 0:T are the stochastic latent states."
  ],
