    "By marrying the strengths of RNNs with the flexibility of State Space Models (SSM) [54], RSSM establishes a comprehensive framework for world models, enhancing their ability to predict future states with a balance of precision and adaptability.We denote the sequence of observations and actions as (x 0, a 1, x 1, a 2, x 2,..., a T, x T)."
